{"tid":1484214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對腳巢皮唔消毒好易生香港腳 返到屋企記得咁做","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:19:51.000Z","uid":220645,"like":144,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"69d7005aeff21a113eab479f78ee752350773557","tid":1484214,"uid":220645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"今日大家行完維園之後對腳應該會因大雨噏住開始巢皮， 好似呢個po咁隔住個mon都聞到陣味：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1483636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1483636</a> （潔癖慎入）。如果唔及時處理過兩日就會患上本地人常見嘅腳部疾病 一 香港腳，會癢到你不停想拗，以下係個人消毒方法：<br />\n<br />\n1) 沖完涼之後攞個浴缸盆裝暖水，高度覆蓋到你全隻腳嘅位置<br />\n2) 落兩大羹鹽<br />\n3) 浸住你雙腳十分鐘<br />\n4) 用紙巾抹乾，確保你全隻腳包括腳趾罅都乾曬為止<br />\n<br />\n祝各位對靚腳保得住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補充多句，行完對臭鞋記得攞去洗，乾咗對鞋啲真菌重會喺到"},{"pid":"4c1c60c56e6c92ba1e27ecf06d3c5856ee8389fe","tid":1484214,"uid":220645,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n5 demands, No one less"},{"pid":"5843049019de0cfae61d40f963104264b4017d3d","tid":1484214,"uid":10722,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727d25eeaebd96d49ec85947ce42d69cae9f370e","tid":1484214,"uid":220645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n5 demands, No one less"},{"pid":"667fb6ca0f03e6b9fbfb5d5115ca10eba696df3c","tid":1484214,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"護腳tips，推<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借推，大學生（急需有去過exchange 嘅學生）請幫個忙填問卷籌錢比612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8nGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=37838a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZU